FIG. 2 is a plane view showing a conventional memory cell structure in which cells patterns are arranged with cell wiring pattern of the 1/4 pitch type folded bit system;


FIG. 3 is a plane view showing a memory cell structure in which cell patterns are arranged with cell wiring pattern of the folded bit system according to a first embodiment of this invention;


FIG. 4 is a diagram showing a relationship between inclined angles and spaces between device region patterns in the memory cell structure illustrated in FIG. 3;


FIG. 5 is a cross sectional view, taken the memory cell layout illustrated in FIG. 3 along X--X line;


FIG. 6 is a plane view showing a memory cell structure in which cells patterns are arranged with cell wiring pattern of the folded bit system according to a second embodiment of this invention; and


FIG. 7 is a plane view showing a memory cell structure in which cells patterns are arranged with cell wiring pattern of the folded bit system according to a third embodiment of this invention.
